      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MICTON MOUSE (9) turned in a good effort at his latest appearance to get home by a narrow margin over 1770m at this track on April 13. May just need a bit of luck at some point from this difficult draw. Big chance in this comparable race. MAJORS CREEK (8) finished second last start over 1770m at this track, beaten 4 metres. Best recent result was a win at Goulburn three starts ago. May need luck at some stage extracting from the inside of the second row. Big chance if she is at her best. FREASON (1) didn't do a bad job when sixth over 1770m at this track last time out. FRESH PRINCE (3) was out of the money two starts ago then things went amiss last start when he copped a check, broke, and finished a long last over 2170m at this track. A nice draw on the front line this time should ensure a cosy run. This doesn't look as hard so he is capable of turning things around.",
